e="backstage-photo"> <div class="mc-column content-media__container"> <div class="content-media-container"> <figure class="content-media__figure"> <img class="content-media__image" srcset="https://s2-techtudo.glbimg.com/He6QP2k_7Yay-bShvHkxe51NkiU=/0x0:695x393/1000x0/smart/filters:strip_icc()/i.s3.glbimg.com/v1/AUTH_08fbf48bc0524877943fe86e43087e7a/internal_photos/bs/2021/1/u/emNkEeTOmWd1wM3W7StA/2013-12-16-abril-de-1999-microsoft.png 1000w, https://s2-techtudo.glbimg.com/HMt450EwJXmB75VVwomuhKfb7MQ=/0x0:695x393/984x0/smart/filters:strip_icc()/i.s3.glbimg.com/v1/AUTH_08fbf48bc0524877943fe86e43087e7a/internal_photos/bs/2021/1/u/emNkEeTOmWd1wM3W7StA/2013-12-16-abril-de-1999-microsoft.png 984w, https://s2-techtudo.glbimg.com/DX814ABaHQ326NbleLQPJ_cqHF0=/0x0:695x393/640x0/smart/filters:strip_icc()/i.s3.glbimg.com/v1/AUTH_08fbf48bc0524877943fe86e43087e7a/internal_photos/bs/2021/1/u/emNkEeTOmWd1wM3W7StA/2013-12-16-abril-de-1999-microsoft.png 640w, https://s2-techtudo.glbimg.com/hjoF80OcazSsy1z0lJUUacEn_gA=/0x0:695x393/600x0/smart/filters:strip_icc()/i.s3.glbimg.com/v1/AUTH_08fbf48bc0524877943fe86e43087e7a/internal_photos/bs/2021/1/u/emNkEeTOmWd1wM3W7StA/2013-12-16-abril-de-1999-microsoft.png 600w" src="https://s2-techtudo.glbimg.com/HMt450EwJXmB75VVwomuhKfb7MQ=/0x0:695x393/984x0/smart/filters:strip_icc()/i.s3.glbimg.com/v1/AUTH_08fbf48bc0524877943fe86e43087e7a/internal_photos/bs/2021/1/u/emNkEeTOmWd1wM3W7StA/2013-12-16-abril-de-1999-microsoft.png" alt="Site da Microsot em abril de 1999  — Foto: Reprodução/Marvin Costa" width="695" height="393" loading="lazy"> <figcaption class="content-media__description"> Site da Microsot em abril de 1999 — Foto: Reprodução/Marvin Costa </figcaption> </figure> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="cropped-block"> <div class="row medium-uncollapsed content-media content-photo" data-block-type="backstage-photo"> <div class="mc-column content-media__container"> <div class="content-media-container"> <figure class="content-media__figure"> <img class="content-media__image" srcset="https://s2-techtudo.glbimg.com/oWyHVXI2HafRiA3XmHlgPurlRPI=/0x0:695x438/1000x0/smart/filters:strip_icc()/i.s3.glbimg.com/v1/AUTH_08fbf48bc0524877943fe86e43087e7a/internal_photos/bs/2021/2/A/Ghi1FVT8GEmth6YxCLHg/2013-12-16-outubro-de-2002-microsoft.png 1000w, https://s2-techtudo.glbimg.com/86BL2NIUXGnkIVcnyvFnlDLOUgM=/0x0:695x438/984x0/smart/filters:strip_icc()/i.s3.glbimg.com/v1/AUTH_08fbf48bc0524877943fe86e43087e7a/internal_photos/bs/2021/2/A/Ghi1FVT8GEmth6YxCLHg/2013-12-16-outubro-de-2002-microsoft.png 984w, https://s2-techtudo.glbimg.com/s7FK0o8YdyjIq_EEnCwg47QytoM=/0x0:695x438/640x0/smart/filters:strip_icc()/i.s3.glbimg.com/v1/AUTH_08fbf48bc0524877943fe86e43087e7a/internal_photos/bs/2021/2/A/Ghi1FVT8GEmth6YxCLHg/2013-12-16-outubro-de-2002-microsoft.png 640w, https://s2-techtudo.glbimg.com/-jpEYAQ4qGES9-HFR0PW7lI1nKo=/0x0:695x438/600x0/smart/filters:strip_icc()/i.s3.glbimg.com/v1/AUTH_08fbf48bc0524877943fe86e43087e7a/internal_photos/bs/2021/2/A/Ghi1FVT8GEmth6YxCLHg/2013-12-16-outubro-de-2002-microsoft.png 600w" src="https://s2-techtudo.glbimg.com/86BL2NIUXGnkIVcnyvFnlDLOUgM=/0x0:695x438/984x0/smart/filters:strip_icc()/i.s3.glbimg.com/v1/AUTH_08fbf48bc0524877943fe86e43087e7a/internal_photos/bs/2021/2/A/Ghi1FVT8GEmth6YxCLHg/2013-12-16-outubro-de-2002-microsoft.png" alt="Site da Microsoft em outubro de 2002  — Foto: Reprodução/Marvin Costa" width="695" height="438" loading="lazy"> <figcaption class="content-media__description"> Site da Microsoft em outubro de 2002 — Foto: Reprodução/Marvin Costa </figcaption> </figure> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="cropped-block"> <div class="mc-column content-text active-extra-styles " data-block-type="unstyled" data-block-weight="58"> <p class=" content-text__container " data-track-category="Link no Texto" data-track-links> Mesmo encontrando diversos tipos de sites de todo o mundo, o Internet Wayback Machine não apresenta nenhum resultado quando uma URL de rede social é buscada. Mesmo assim, ele pode garantir bons momentos de diversão e colaborar com pesquisas e estudos sobre o desenvolvimento do web design e revelar dados importantes sobre diversas companhias de tecnologia e blogs. </p> </div> </div> <div class="cropped-block"> <div class="mc-column content-text active-extra-styles " data-block-type="unstyled" data-block-weight="12"> <p class=" content-text__container " data-track-category="Link no Texto" data-track-links> <em>Veja mais: aprenda a visualizar os sites que quiser sem deixar rastros.</em> </p> </div> </div> <div class="cropped-block"> <div class="bs-video-block mc-column  content-media content-video" data-block-type="backstage-video" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/VideoObject" itemprop="video"> <div class="content-media__container "> <meta itemprop="embedUrl" content="https://s.videos.globo.com/p3/amp/index.html?videosIDs=8629504&adUnit=edtechtudo%2FSoftwares&adCustomData=advertiser%3Dcoca-cola%2Ccolgate%2Cfacilidades%2Capple%2Cunilever%2Cheineken&adCmsId=&adAccountId=85042905&ga_productUA=UA-156625-22&ga_extras=%7B%22dimension1%22%3A%22%25%28channel%29s%22%7D&domain=www.techtudo.com.br&ambient=%25%28channel%29s&origin_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.techtudo.com.br%2Fdicas-e-tutoriais%2F2013%2F12%2Fcomo-visualizar-versoes-antigas-de-sites-e-encontrar-paginas-fora-do-ar.ghtml"> <meta itemprop="name" content="Saiba como navegar na Internet de modo anônimo ou sem deixar rastros"> <meta itemprop="thumbnailUrl" content="https://s01.video.glbimg.com/x240/8629504.jpg"> <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="2013-12-16T18:33:18.030000Z"> <meta itemprop="uploadDate" content="2013-12-16T18:33:18.030000Z"> <div class="content-video__bigger-player-description-fixer"> <article class="content-video"> <section class="content-video__video-container"> <div class="content-video__video"> <div class="content-video__placeholder" data-video-id="8629504" data-autoplay="true" data-video-orientation="horizontal"> <img class="content-video__placeholder_